{"tid":2022380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲天空寫出「Taiwan Can Help」，台灣人淚崩感謝澳洲","createTime":"2020-05-18T09:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T14:52:30.000Z","uid":52658,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"41f8bc74decefe8fc5f611e2a18fa60813ae50e6","tid":2022380,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0SPkCW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0SPkCW.jpg&h=4a631c5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坎培拉的天空今天傍晚出現TAIWAN CAN HELP的訊息，許多民眾好奇抬頭看，並拿手機拍照。旅澳台裔醫師發起這場天空寫字活動，爭取台灣加入世衛組織，有澳洲聯邦眾議員到場聲援。<br />\n<br />\n第二場天空寫字活動明天將在雪梨舉行。林占峰指出，作為醫生，他相信每個人都應受公平對待，不論種族、國籍或政治立場。WHO將台灣排除在外，對台灣不公平，抗疫需要全球合作，WHO不應排除任何國家、任何人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sa5M7ia.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsa5M7ia.png&h=9ab032e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4647dd20b48868e5744798debdfbb40e4c37a602","tid":2022380,"uid":14494,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:47:59.000Z","msg":"how？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796a57e51c3fa9cf5a82e104f836400cff755856","tid":2022380,"uid":22362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"Taiwan No. 1"},{"pid":"6f865daccc4302b7c006615c2d72f274f0234a21","tid":2022380,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d4143d35e53e62f8e3f0a2dbddf03fea2113c7d","tid":2022380,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"676b61d2d0f2a27ccad477b789264712c1fa2a3a","tid":2022380,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d4143d35e53e62f8e3f0a2dbddf03fea2113c7d","tid":2022380,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4647dd2